init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: My dad was the 1.6 billionth best dad in the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I know that he loves me and that he is trying his best.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I know that my dad will never be the best dad in the world, but he is the best dad for me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I wanted to show him that I loved him and that I was proud of him.
